1.0.name: wordpress/baw-autoshortener
1.0.description: AutoShortener can create short links in your WordPress website for your posts and pages but also for external links. You got many many great options, a usefull admin panel, bookmarklets, shorcodes. But easy to use ! Visit website http://www.autoshort.com for more informations.
